name: ArrayStack_popTest
description: Unit tests for the pop functionality of the ArrayStack class.

test_cases.name: testPopWithItems
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality of the ArrayStack when there are items in the stack.

test_cases.name: testPopOnEmptyStack
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality of the ArrayStack when the stack is empty, expecting an EmptyStackException.

test_cases.name: testPopAfterPeek
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality of the ArrayStack after a peek operation.

test_cases.name: testPopAndSearch
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality of the ArrayStack in conjunction with the search method.

test_cases.name: testPopAndEmpty
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality of the ArrayStack and checks if the stack becomes empty after the pop operation.
